    Create New Product        ${product_json}

    Set Test Variable         ${product_json}

Quando solicito a exclusão
    Click Element   xpath://tr[td//text()[contains(., '${product_json['name']}')]]//button
    Wait Until Element Is Visible   class:swal2-modal

